headline: CoreWeave's Q2 Loss Narrows Y/Y, Revenues Up, Stock Down
summary: CRWV posts narrower Q2 loss, record revenue surge of 207% on AI-cloud demand. It lifts 2025 revenue outlook amid major customer wins.
